# NOTE: api/*.mjs (esbuild output of `npm run build:api`) ARE committed.
# They must exist in the repo at clone time because Vercel validates the
# `functions` patterns in vercel.json against the cloned api/ dir BEFORE
# running the build command. Gitignoring them broke every prod deploy
# (commit 0572257). Run `npm run build:api` and commit the result when
# any src/api/*.ts changes.
